issue.title: Sending to the Callback Endpoint while proxying through ZAP logs an error

milestone.description: Enhancements and bug fixes expected to be included in a following main release.

repository.name: zaproxy
repository.description: The ZAP by Checkmarx Core project

issue.body:
If you are proxying through ZAP and send something to the Callback Endpoint on HTTP there is the follwing Exception:

```
ZAP Error [org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpMalformedHeaderException]: Failed to find pattern: (HTTP/\d+\.\d+) +(\d{3}) *([^\x00-\x1f\r\n]*)

Stack Trace:
org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpMalformedHeaderException: Failed to find pattern: (HTTP/\d+\.\d+) +(\d{3}) *([^\x00-\x1f\r\n]*)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpResponseHeader.parse(HttpResponseHeader.java:119)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpResponseHeader.setMessage(HttpResponseHeader.java:94)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpHeader.<init>(HttpHeader.java:146)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpResponseHeader.<init>(HttpResponseHeader.java:78)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpMethodHelper.getHttpResponseHeader(HttpMethodHelper.java:282)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpSender.send(HttpSender.java:514)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpSender.sendAuthenticated(HttpSender.java:490)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpSender.sendAuthenticated(HttpSender.java:479)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpSender.sendAndReceive(HttpSender.java:394)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.network.HttpSender.sendAndReceive(HttpSender.java:351)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.core.proxy.ProxyThread.processHttp(ProxyThread.java:509)
	at org.parosproxy.paros.core.proxy.ProxyThread.run(ProxyThread.java:317)
	at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:748)
```

If you use HTTPS with an IpAddress there is additionally a "ERR_CERT_COMMON_NAME_INVALID" problem before the HttpMalformedHeaderException.
